column5: LOL....That'd work on Brook as long as I don't throw it in the water, she hates the water.
I can teach her to swim,just send her down here.I promise to give her back.NOT.I think Rick posted this a few years back but I just came back across it. Joe
i find that a old rapala with no treble hooks works just as well but some times you need to switch it up

Sorry Joe, after she got away from me last week, I ended up finding her sitting at the side door waiting for me (Art knows the details), I'd have to say she's firmly attached to me she'd likely bolt her way back to Canada. But I'd be happy to let you visit with her at Lakair.
Nope, sorry, beg to differ. With Pops house and the farm she would be more than happy here......    Art
